- bouton "Supprimer" (apres lecture) =>
  1) archive en localStorage (admin_message_history)
  2) DELETE /api/contact/{id}

4.4 Produits
- liste produits via GET /api/admin/products
- ajout via POST /api/admin/products
- edition via PUT /api/admin/products/{id}
- suppression via DELETE /api/admin/products/{id}
